*.log
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# WebView2's per-app browser profile (History, Login Data, Web Data,
# Cookies — real Chromium user-data files, not app code). Already covered
# by bin/ above for git purposes, but this got leaked once via the
# separate release-zip packaging step, which zips files directly and does
# NOT go through git or this file at all. Any release build script MUST
# explicitly exclude *.WebView2/ (or publish from a directory that never
# ran the app, so this folder never exists in the first place) — this
# gitignore entry alone does not protect a release zip.
*.WebView2/
